Item 2: Cultural Policy
A. Core Values
  We want our company 
  have our employees come to work with the sense that they are safe and valued. We believe that people do their best work
  when they are safe and comfortable. Everyone from every walk of life will find an inclusive and judgment free workspace with us. We
  want the world to recognize us as the company with the happiest employees.
  

B. Motivation
  We love it when employees can work and socialize comfortably in the workplace.
  We are afraid of a hostile and inefficient workplace.

C. Summary



